                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17419805" author="gson" created="Fri, 24 Sep 2021 14:16:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is logically equivalent to the behavior described in&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3151&quot; title=&quot;Messages get logged at level OFF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-3151&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-3151&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2174&quot; title=&quot;EventLogger#logEvent() Incorrect documentation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-2174&quot;&gt;LOG4J2-2174&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;br/&gt;
 Thus, I am aware of the logic in the internal filter method. The documentation, on the other hand, put me on the wrong track of how to use the levels.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17420376" author="vy" created="Sun, 26 Sep 2021 20:26:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;As stated in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3151&quot; title=&quot;Messages get logged at level OFF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-3151&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-3151&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, we are aware of this shortcoming of the documentation and PRs improving this state are more than welcome.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17420415" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Mon, 27 Sep 2021 00:10:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You are correct that there is an error in the table that maps the LoggerConfig Level to the event Level.&#160; When the LoggerConfig Level is &quot;OFF&quot; both the &quot;ALL&quot; and &quot;OFF&quot; event levels should be YES.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17453770" author="jira-bot" created="Mon, 6 Dec 2021 03:46:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 22a96e36e111c5f24798e36c236121093a8baa9e in logging-log4j2&apos;s branch refs/heads/master from Ralph Goers&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=22a96e3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=22a96e3&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

