[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=2505210&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gitbox.apache.org/repos/asf?p=logging-log4j2.git;h=2505210&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-3166&quot; title=&quot;wrong documentation for logging with Level.OFF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LOG4J2-3166&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LOG4J2-3166&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; - Fix log event Level vs LoggerConfig Level table.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
